      },
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "几天后，暴风雨过去了——",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-1",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "不出所料，樱花尽数凋谢，零落而污脏的樱花瓣乱糟糟地铺满了这片土地。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "actor": 306070,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 5,
      "say": "指挥官今天也来了吗。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "{namecode:78}她有任务暂时离开了……要等等她吗？",
      "actor": 306070,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "对{namecode:179}说没事后，走向了原本要和{namecode:78}约会的路线。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 0.5,
        "dur": 0.5
      },
      "say": "走近樱花林后发现，这里的情况比之前见到的要更糟——道路上随处可见折断的树枝，一片狼藉。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "flashout": {
        "alpha": [
          0,
          1
        ],
        "black": true,
        "dur": 0.5
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "指挥官，这条路线现在禁止通行。",
      "actor": 301580,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "如你所见，我们正在清理这里的残枝落叶，请先离开吧。",
      "actor": 301580,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "……那根樱花树枝怎么了吗？",
      "actor": 301580,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "say": "这根樱花树枝，也许可以……",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_main_twilight"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 0.5,
        "dur": 0.5
      },
      "say": "几天后——",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "flashout": {
        "alpha": [
          0,
          1
        ],
        "black": true,
        "dur": 0.5
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "（本以为要有一段时间和殿下见不了面了，没想到却收到了一封希望我来办公室一趟的邮件……）",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "（从暴风雨那天算起，这是第一次见面吗……不，我也不能一直因过去的事而愁眉苦脸呢。）",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "殿下，打扰了——",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "{namecode:78}敲了敲门，轻轻地走进了办公室。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "殿下，好久不见了。因为一直在执行任务，没能跟您打上招呼……",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "殿下，这个花瓶里——难道是樱花枝？",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "{namecode:78}惊讶地望着插在花瓶里的樱花树枝。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "其实那天{namecode:28}打扫的树枝中，有一枝还长着几个未开的花蕾。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "当时想着，如果稍加培养的话说不定能开出花——结果天随人愿，办公室里绽放出盛开的樱花。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "您是……想把这个给我看吗?",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "您在邮件里说……有无论如何都想和我一起看的东西……",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "{namecode:78}凝视着美丽的樱花树枝，将手紧紧贴在胸前。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "谢谢您，殿下……",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "没想到……看到这个，自己会是那么的开心……",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "即使我是不幸的体质，殿下也能像这样带给我各种小小的幸福……",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "我现在，一定比任何人都要更幸福呢……",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "看着她望向这边的湿润的眼瞳，我不假思索地握住了她的手。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "也许今后还会发生各种幸福与不幸的事，但我希望{namecode:78}每次都能发自内心地微笑出来。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "哪怕是最微小的幸福，我也想全部分享给她。",
      "blackBg": true,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    }
  ],
